=Rumors (a work in progress!)=

Welcome to the Rumors page! 

GMs can use this page to quickly produce evocative ‘facts’ about their worlds. Written for no particular setting, the goal was only to create, through whispers and oblique suggestions, a world that would be fun to adventure and intrigue in, making it widely applicable to (and hopefully not too generic for) nearly any fantasy environment.

Mythology and the history of antiquity inspired much of the content, with some twists; I steer more towards literary content than game mechanics, but I know as a GM what inspired me most were always simple ideas I could flesh out and run with, so I offer these in that same spirit: may these rumors provide a spark that lets your creativity mold something memorable at the game table.

